race.description: Bull Creek Beef Country Stampede Qualifier Hcp
race.comment: Good race but impossible to go past YUKAN ROSE (6) who remains unbeaten in two starts for the new yard. Drawn well and expect she'll take a camp off the lead here. Take beating again with winning rider staying aboard. SANTORINI SUN (7) was off her best last time but the start prior was an open class winner here. Gets a chance to bounce back. MR METRICS (1) was a Townsville winner last time and will give a sight again. YOUR TOO GOOD (5) has been building to a win with back-to-back seconds and another bold showing is expected. THERESABEARINTHERE (4) is consistent and is next best. Has good early speed and loves this short trip.
